dct_title_s: Partial view of the city of Havana
dct_description_sm: Map shows roads and important landmarks represented pictorially. "Zanja entre Galiano y Aguila." "Pizarra Rotativa Telef.: A-2991." On verso: photographs, 1953 calendar, and lists of holidays, birth stones, and wedding anniversary gifts.
